Print a list of instructors displaying 'Less Salary' if less than 72000 if exactly 72000 display as 'Exact Salary' and if greater than 

select name, salary,
	case 
		when salary < 72000 then 'less salary'
		when salary = 72000 then 'exact salary'
		else 'more salary'
		end as salary_catagory
	from instructor;

Display names of all the instructors concatenated with their department names.

select i.name || ' - ' || d.name from instructor i join department d on i.dept_id=d.dept_id;
